Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.84,0:00:16.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.21,0:00:20.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點來啊 賓果! 中大獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:27.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿面笑容 PicoPico 一口氣飛到月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.09,0:00:33.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天一餐 活力充沛 喝牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.00,0:00:39.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是外星人也能輕鬆發出電波交朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古今東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回憶是熱帶地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.01,0:00:48.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威夷衫好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.25,0:00:55.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕緊破涕為笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.68,0:00:59.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從石頭開始猜拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.22,0:01:01.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊張刺激的雲霄飛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛和勇氣和夢想紙摺扇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.52,0:01:09.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心的渦輪加速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:10.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bang！Bang！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.03,0:01:12.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃吧 瘋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.40,0:01:13.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:16.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暢行無阻的護照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿戲劇性又浪漫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.34,0:01:25.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,By VOYOOFPDK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.10,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨機法國料理省略甜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草莓鮮奶油蛋糕 草莓一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.07,0:01:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧克力蛋糕 巧克力一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起司蛋糕 起司一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,栗子泥蛋糕 栗子 栗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.15,0:01:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好吃的栗子泥蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己做的蛋糕不曉得大家喜不喜歡吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望可以靠這些提高一點天使隊的風評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會議已經開始了我得快一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 梅爾優那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼重要的時刻她跑到哪裡摸魚去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛 真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部到齊了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.46,0:02:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名單上 除了華克中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.16,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫著還有五名隊員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.50,0:02:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 還有一個 她馬上就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會議開始的時間早就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊的隊員連時間都無法遵守啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來 如果軍方有人提出解散意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.02,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只能默默的接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶好耶 棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這個危機是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去 真的會被解散的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優會不會忘了要開會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.41,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才她還在廚房做蛋糕 說要拿到會議上來給大家吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.51,0:03:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都溫泉迷霧蛋糕殺人事件發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼辦？中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我去叫她來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優究竟在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.06,0:03:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不在天使屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會想到這種蠢主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華克中校到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要解散至少也要給遣散費嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕上了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是梅爾優櫻葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果還是沒找到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他也太扯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來天使隊真的得解散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的美少女偶像生活也只能到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是梅爾優？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種怪模怪樣的變裝五秒鐘就會被拆穿的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣太失禮了 可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要說七秒鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快點坐好 梅爾優櫻葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我坐好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 為什麼沒被拆穿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇跡出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 會議開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.54,0:05:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才我也跟華克中校說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有中校 會議是無法開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.49,0:05:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要展現我愛護天使隊的心意給大家看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 請開始會議吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這實在太扯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包准會被拆穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.41,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是 角色根本就不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 那麼 華克中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來轉達關於基地內對天使隊的否定意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先關於經費方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要花這麼多錢呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是伙食費的金額太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為義工活動的一環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們做了很多甜點送給戰地困苦的外星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們好喜歡吃我親手做的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼跟什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定我們現在正在見証歷史的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.72,0:07:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特 我感動到連眼淚都流出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊連這種義行都在做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是值得誇獎的偉大行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡 您太過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是做了應該做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.81,0:07:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪了 剛才去叫中校的人好像還沒回來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.11,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對哦 這次換薄荷布拉曼修沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去叫她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷很難搞定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是薄荷布拉曼修我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事主旨好像漸漸偏離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她耳朵太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.84,0:07:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 那些耳朵的數目正是香草愛天使隊的証明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.29,0:08:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們繼續吧 經費的事就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我看了你們的行動記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.36,0:08:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草亞修為什麼你老是去教會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草亞修也沒有回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是香草亞修 我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來 香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下會議可以開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是棒極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.08,0:08:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你們不要一直讓我講同樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花法蘭波瓦茲怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於輪到我出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是蘭花法蘭波瓦茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜...拜托 你化的妝跟造型是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是蘭花啊 蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不是這麼噁心的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.84,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？我倒是覺得蠻像的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去叫佛特修特倫來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是佛特修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是什麼德行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼德行？我是佛特啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別扯了！基本上外形就不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的身材也沒有這麼沒水準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想打架嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰怕誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就想跟你分個高下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.27,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等...等等 請你們兩個不要打啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兔子耳朵 兔子耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好迷人喔 香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會議中吵什麼吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草亞修在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請...請稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她馬上就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去叫她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.74,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 這是個好辦法這次換大家變回自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就不用吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是個好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次由我們去叫香草回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為從剛才看到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要去叫的人就不會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼讓貝洛兄弟去叫香草亞修回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慘兮兮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 天使隊的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問香草在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們帶你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只要好好監視就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是天使隊的香草亞修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.34,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有附送的 諾麥德2號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.58,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來天使隊終於全都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就繼續進行會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做的蛋糕這麼好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫著"請多指教"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這棟大樓是剛蓋好的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說以前都是坐著的嗎？("蓋好"音近"站著")
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼坐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跪坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優 大樓不會跪坐的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼是蹲著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托著下巴盤腿坐著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.12,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是跟你說了它不會坐的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.36,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是躺著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.92,0:12:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趴著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不 不會趴也不會躺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草獲得一個坐墊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請繼續欣賞下半集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特制前菜省略主菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 下一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃 看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬥犬 15級結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕鬆過關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,27秒擊落全機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的功力大增了不少 可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 是敵人太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是模擬訓練嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方只不過是電腦程式 贏了當然沒什麼好驕傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且晃動得太厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不稍微平靜一點的話 我會無法集中精神看書的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.16,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 你就只知道看書根本不訓練 你有什麼資格講我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也過關了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰略模擬訓練20級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20級？你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最高級不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.04,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管15級還是20級 反正都只是模擬訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.38,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是藉著平日的訓練累積提高任務的成功率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.62,0:13:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是從小就接受訓練的一流軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那種莫名其妙的七拼八湊天使隊是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待你們的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以囉 反正模擬訓練也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去吃頓聖代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛啦？少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.84,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本沒聽懂我在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來還有軍隊規定的訓練課程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准擅自行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.88,0:14:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 訓練是給蠢材做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.42,0:14:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們兩個是完美的超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.22,0:14:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不用訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.56,0:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過今後的任務我們確定不會失敗的比率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於天使隊的再度結隊已經降到45％了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這樣 我們還是不需要訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來好像是白費力氣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是日積月累就會呈現出它的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人說的話一定要聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又把我們當小孩子看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你們本來就是小孩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡我最討厭被人家當小孩看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就直闖司令部証明我們的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 好 我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們繼續做下一個訓練課程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你想背叛我嗎？你不想吃聖代了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是乖乖去做訓練吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.14,0:15:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們是聽話的乖小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來回30公里結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能力方面是沒話說 不過就是太孩子氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼鬼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是兒童套餐嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要吃這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過挺好吃的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是好不好吃的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是新開發的幼兒營養食品試吃實習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖的吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.33,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,營養均衡 容易消化吸收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用擔心蛀牙的問題 是很棒的食物喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然老是把我當小孩看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫 給我等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在悠哉的吃什麼啊？你也跟我一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啦 我還沒吃完耶
