Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餓扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要逃出來也應該吃飽飯再逃啊
