Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰要向她道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的確很了不起啊 梅琳少校畢竟是少校
